Package org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.apacheatlas.resource

package org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.apacheatlas.resource
The Apache Atlas REST connector provides a java interface to the Apache Atlas server. It is a resource connector.
